Description: Condition: This Jackson Dinky in Natural Ash has been very gently used, and is in excellent condition with little to no signs of wear. Serial number: MXJ1607170. Weight: 7.38 lbs. The Jackson Pro Series Dinky DK3 features an ash body, a 1-piece maple neck with graphite reinforcement, a 12"-16" compound radius, and an ebony fretboard. It's stacked with a Seymour Duncan JB TB-4 humbucker in the bridge position, and Seymour Duncan Custom Flat Strat SSL-6 single coils in the middle and neck positions. It's also equipped with a Floyd Rose FRT 02000 locking tremolo system.
